a:5:{s:5:"title";s:45:"Spiro separates Merge and Delete permissions";s:16:"text-format-info";a:3:{s:10:"text-final";s:355:"<p>Spiro now treats merge and delete as distinct permissions. This allows admins to delegate deduplication/cleanup workflows (merge) while restricting irreversible actions (delete).</p>
<p>Learn more here: <a href="https://support.spiro.ai/article/648-spiro-release-january-2026">https://support.spiro.ai/article/648-spiro-release-january-2026</a></p>
